  <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3"><strong>44% of UK SME websites lack basic Organization schema</strong> - This represents a significant competitive advantage for businesses that implement comprehensive structured data strategies.</li>
  <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3"><strong>FAQPage schema delivers immediate AI visibility improvements</strong> - The Q&A format matches how users interact with AI assistants, making extraction simple and accurate.</li>
  <li class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3"><strong>Implementation priority: Organization, LocalBusiness, FAQPage</strong> - Start with foundational schema types before moving to advanced markup for specific content and services.</li>
